{"type": "article", "id": 62764, "title": "这套布艺封皮的笔记本，纹理质感都很有艺术气息｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-04-08T23:12:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 57771, "name": "Thomas Vailly"}, {"id": 14845, "name": "Foster + Partners"}, {"id": 16270, "name": "Industrial Facility"}, {"id": 57772, "name": "Gabriel Scott"}, {"id": 22260, "name": "EOS"}, {"id": 57773, "name": "Shapeways"}, {"id": 57774, "name": "JNBYHOME"}, {"id": 23568, "name": "Konstantin Grcic"}, {"id": 939, "name": "Jasper Morrison"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190408201421Qzt76xE23ufKNRoJ.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} </style>  </p><h3>Lab-Replay Notebook by JNBYHOME</h3><p>NOTABOOK 是 JNBYHOME 的笔记本系列，如同系列名所表达的：这是一个充满奇趣的笔记本，却又不仅仅是笔记本。它能够在使用过程中积累主人深浅不一的痕迹，而产生不同的风格记忆。这一季设计融入 Replay 的设计灵感，首次推出采用小黑屋面料的布艺笔记本系列。</p><p>极具春日气息的湖绿与亮橙成为封皮的主打颜色。它们给人一种恰到好处的“清醒感”。设计师利用 JNBY 集团的高定库存面料及“小黑屋”开发的实验面料来取代往季的牛皮材质，使其在触感上有更加丰富的体验，纹样也更加独特。</p><p>这款封皮便是由“小黑屋”里一台半自动老式有梭多臂织机开发而成。由于手工织造的随机性与创造性，最终的成品呈现分明的纹理质感，封皮的不规则毛边切割设计更是增添了艺术气息。</p><p>内芯本选用意大利 85g Fedrigoni 双胶纸，手感紧密富有韧性。精细的过胶工艺使每一页都可平铺书写，无论是在嘈杂的会议室，狭窄拥挤的机舱，或颠簸的火车上，你都可以自然随意地记录。</p><p>除了没有限定的空白本之外，还设有点阵、网格等功能型內芯，既能够天马行空地自由涂画，也能够满足设计制图所需。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904082034538XCJvtn0oSVU1yDA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203455GqlL4u7dHavzJ0Eb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904082034533CBKHaiYcEnTvAj6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203456DnSlb6xrvKT0tJog.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203456JPxiSlQVNkKXuCwd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203457A2HPO9E5dvWGDJNL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203457HqZJkYe7TaSj0mfp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203457aux1Ah0TVcXLZnEs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203458kji9K72roeYnqGN0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PA11 by Shapeways &amp; EOS</h3><p>最近，总部位于纽约的 3D 打印制造商 Shapeways 与工业 3D 打印团队 EOS 开展合作，为设计师和企业提供市场准入的矫形器和假体结局方案 PA11，这是一种来自蓖麻油的生物降解尼龙材料。</p><p>医疗市场需要经济实惠的材料来制造牙箍和假肢等部件。PA11 的推出将为 Shapeways 与医疗从业者合作打开大门，将 3D 打印技术应用于定制医疗。</p><p>PA11 材料来源于蓖麻油，以其弹性和抗冲击尼龙特性而闻名。PA11 具有更高的强度和柔韧性，是一种抗冲击和延展性材料，具有高断裂伸长率。PA11 适用于活动、可穿戴物品和按扣，适合零件和铰链，非常适用于高冲击力的定制零件，如假肢、牙套、鞋垫和其他外部医疗需求。PA11 将以天然白色涂层提供，也可以染成任何所需的颜色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203530zSoaKwY63hOQH5kb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.482812\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203530QhoTcRg3EWLMf1XG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.482812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203530iAaZHQehxTwf5Ejq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.482812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203530F48n6rl7IVbUCZXe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203531h6fjUc5uEQJ1SNos.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203531OhREbKCS37pil1cB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203533euj2XFY1xzPIGW3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.shapeways.com/partnership/pa11\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shapeways</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>LUNA Lighting System by Gabriel Scott</h3><p>黄铜、铁、玻璃等寻常人眼中的冷峻材质，在加拿大的 GabrielKakon 和 ScottRichler 两兄弟的手中却可以呈现出如珠宝般迷人的光芒。</p><p>最近，两人推出了新的照明系统 LUNA 。据称整个系列的灵感来源于月球光晕或是月亮的漫射光。</p><p>这种模块化灯具可根据组装形式水平或垂直向搭配。柔和色彩，硬朗的线条和曲线形状的混合，以及它创造的折射光都完美融合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203653N3JLWgpyRu06TtXS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.781481\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203653SCYnXJucEkxKVLZg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203654r1nkfT8IeZc34Ml0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203654Wnu2RUKloXmk69Az.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203654Pj0ts6WNYvrDK98b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.448148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203654DhIGK7CPgWMnYtoE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203655zPJ6VWRgoNAjcmvw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203656pcyszQDJvxXIq83H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203656fiMGo2rZgzdjYUV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772840\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.gabriel-scott.com/luna-series\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gabriel Scott</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>New Seating Collections by Jasper Morrison, Konstantin Grcic, Foster + Partners and Industrial Facility for Mattiazzi</h3><p>为庆祝品牌创立 10 周年，意大利家具品牌 Mattiazzi 推出了四个新系列的座椅，请来包括 Jasper Morrison，Konstantin Grcic，Foster + Partners 和 Industrial Facility 在内的设计师或者工作室。</p><p>四个新系列将在米兰设计周上推出。</p><p>Industrial Facility 设计了由松木和钢制成的椅子和矮凳，将其命名为 Fronda。英国设计师 Jasper Morrison 的 Zampa 系列包括灰木矮凳和高凳。Konstantin Grcic 的 Cugino 凳子，采用厚实的圆形顶部和三脚底座，是用实心橡木制成。</p><p>Foster + Partners 的第四个系列 Leva 是灰木椅，其灵感来自于桨的形状。“椅子仍然是典型的家具，也是最难设计的物品之一，需要对形状和舒适性有深刻的理解，” Foster + Partners 工业设计主管 Mike Holland 表示。“它必须令人赏心悦目，能够适应从客厅到餐厅的各种环境，舒适地坐着，并且能够持久耐用。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203751e2LY8qIEf3trwkng.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750423\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203752KPYvr4yeVsMJCoD6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.103215\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203751qlcWi72O5nMPa9Hf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728849\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203754hqRprDK3T0AIofVF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.350677\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203754UtOBX5GmQousMpv0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.212352\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203754i5L6hpF48kGStRyZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.213621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203754EaLJsRnUbZduwABh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203755Kt2v6yuxWMhPa5UI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203755hgsOkCLFBnymJDpY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.925973\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.mattiazzi.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mattiazzi</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>SUNFLOWER ENTREPRISE © by Thomas Vailly</h3><p>埃因霍温设计工作室 Thomas Vailly 探索将向日葵转化为一种新型生物可降解材料。从一个小小的螺丝钉，到大型的绝缘板、甚至是智能手机外壳，这些废弃物品曾经无数次被考虑应用在各种各样的应用之中。 </p><p>种植向日葵是为了产油、播种或是用于生物燃料。将油榨取干净后，向日葵的一部分被用来作为动物饲料，但大多数的向日葵“压榨饼”仍是没有被完全的利用。向日葵秆的泡沫结构、外皮的高强度纤维以及花朵的深褐色蛋白均被遗弃。这种农业垃圾事实上可以是非常珍贵的资源，用于生产全新的生物材料。</p><p>收获花朵果实一个月后，外皮纤维与主干泡沫结构分离。纤维经过加热压缩变为硬质纤维板，主干结构经过处理后则作为聚苯乙烯的天然替代材料。这些不同的生物材料外层涂上了一层向日葵光泽面，增强了材料的耐水性，同时从种子提取而来的胶是将这些材料组合起来的最完美的粘合剂。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408204257Yug2GZnTUHdSJX8K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771388\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408204011jYTSyEh6MpWKfCmF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563029\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203952Uc1kK7CSOsAMjhJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584602\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190408203952VThEcBHY3UqaM2Am.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584602\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/04/05/thomas-vailly-sunflower-material/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}